scripts.blueprint:updatecss: mkdir -p public/styles/blueprint-icons/lib/css && cp node_modules/@blueprintjs/core/lib/css/blueprint.css public/styles/ && cp node_modules/@blueprintjs/icons/lib/css/blueprint-icons.css public/styles/blueprint-icons/lib/css/blueprint-icons.css && cp -r node_modules/@blueprintjs/icons/resources public/styles/blueprint-icons/ && cp node_modules/normalize.css/normalize.css public/styles/normalize.css
scripts.ag-grid:updatecss: mkdir -p public/styles && cp node_modules/ag-grid-community/dist/styles/ag-grid.css public/styles/ && cp node_modules/ag-grid-community/dist/styles/ag-theme-alpine.css public/styles/
scripts.postinstall: npm run blueprint:updatecss && npm run ag-grid:updatecss
